data.description: **Seller offering $5,000 in concessions for Buyer closing closts / Rate buy down**.  Well kept house in great location on a peaceful street with tons of development in the area.  There is tons of commercial building on Madison St, a short walk from this home to include multiple restaurants, Convenience store, multiple gyms, furniture store, pet store, nail salon, and various medical centers.  New HVAC in 2021. Updated electric panel with generator connection. New insulation in attic.  The roof is believed to be roughly 10 years old.  New carpet and flooring in living room, kitchen, dining room, and 2 bedrooms. Full partially finished basement. Seller is open to taking down or leaving Shed in back and tree house.
